- **Economics and dispute design** in **`PRODUCT_SPEC.md`** are **canonical**. If **code and spec diverge**, **do not silently edit the spec to match code** — **flag in bold** for a human architect (same norm as **`.cursor/skills/doc-sync/SKILL.md`**).
